name: Google Earth Blog
tag_list: google-earth, gps, gis, journalism, publishing, technology
overview: Google Earth Blog is a resource for learning the latest news about Google Earth, including new applications, interesting sights, latest technology, and resources for learning how to make the most of this fabulous 3D geographic browser. Google Earth Blog provides daily information including when new releases of Google Earth come out, releases of new imagery and layers, describes new technologies and features, or reveals hidden tricks and features. There is way more to Google Earth than just satellite photos. Google Earth Blog describes how you can use Google Earth as a mapping tool, weather forecasting tool, astronomy program, flight simulator, storm tracker, online business medium, GPS tracker, photo geotagger, gaming interface, travel planner, travel journal, and more.
